Private Sub Button_MultiStepConfig_Released() Const MaxStepsOnPage = 16
Dim MaxIndex As Integer MaxIndex = Me.MaxStepNumericDisplay.Value
' Get the parameters passed to the screen Dim Pound As StringList Set Pound = Me.TagParameters
' Get the next index from the display Dim NextIndex As Integer NextIndex = Me.NextStepTextBox.Text
' Validate the input NextIndex If ((NextIndex + MaxStepsOnPage - 1) > MaxIndex) Then ' Went too far, back up NextIndex = MaxIndex - (MaxStepsOnPage - 1) End If If (NextIndex < 1) Then ' Went too far, back up NextIndex = 1 End If
' build the display command Dim sCmd As String Dim i As Integer sCmd = "Display (RA-Seq) P_Seq-Config-MultiStep /T" & Pound(1) & "," & Pound(2)
' Append all of the index parameters For i = 1 To MaxStepsOnPage If (NextIndex <= MaxIndex) Then sCmd = sCmd & "," & CStr(NextIndex) Else sCmd = sCmd & ",0" End If NextIndex = NextIndex + 1 Next i
' Execute the view command Me.Application.ExecuteCommand sCmd End Sub
